@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@rekapBackupUrl = {{baseUrl}}/rekap-backup

### 0. Login & Ambil Token (Jalankan ini Pertama Kali)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Set Variable Token (otomatis diambil dari response login di atas)
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJhZG1pbiIsInJvbGUiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc3Nzg2NTc5MSwiZXhwIjoxNzc3OTUyMTkxfQ.JoN-Tf7aszbfr2AmBs_XVTH-3MvJQU0jG1M2U7gWgFM


### =========================================================
### REKAP BACKUP ENDPOINTS (Wajib jalankan login terlebih dulu)
### =========================================================

### 1. Trigger Full Sync JSON dari Database (Admin)
# Endpoint ini akan menyalin data dari database MySQL ke file JSON lokal (Staging)
POST {{rekapBackupUrl}}/staging/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Manual Sync Toko Aktif (WRC) per Cabang & Periode
# Digunakan untuk menghitung ulang toko aktif dari WRC dan me-replace data JSON
POST {{rekapBackupUrl}}/sync-wrc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "cabang": "G033",
  "periode": "202401"
}

###

### 3. Get Summary Data
# Mengambil rangkuman data harian dan bulanan per cabang
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get Available Years
# Mengambil rentang tahun (oldest dan newest) dari data staging
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/years
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Get Resume Harian per Cabang
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/harian/resume/G001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Get Resume Bulanan per Cabang
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/bulanan/resume/G001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Get Detail Logs Harian
# (Parameter: cabang / periode / kriteria)
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/harian/detail/G001/202401/OK
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Get Detail Logs Bulanan
# (Parameter: cabang / periode / kriteria)
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/bulanan/detail/G001/202401/OK
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Export Excel Data
# Mengunduh file Excel (Uji coba di browser disarankan untuk format blob)
GET {{rekapBackupUrl}}/export?cabang=G001&startYear=2024&endYear=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
